1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:03,260
Brat.

3
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:05,660
It's your turn.

4
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:08,940
Huo Kaiming.

5
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:10,500
What are you doing?

6
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:13,060
You said you'd let us go after
I brought Yang Baichun here.

7
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:16,940
What do you want?

8
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:18,620
Say something!

9
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,100
Huo Kaiming!

10
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:23,950
Curse you!

11
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:25,060
You went back on your word!

12
00:02:25,060 --> 00:02:26,060
What do you want?

13
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:27,860
Huo Kaiming!

14
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:40,660
Songge, run!

15
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:44,900
Huo Kaiming.

16
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:46,060
Don't hurt Songge!

17
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:46,900
Come at me!

18
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:51,060
Huo Kaiming!

19
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:53,860
Huo Kaiming!

20
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:54,860
Come at me!

21
00:02:58,500 --> 00:02:59,340
Huo Kaiming.

22
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,820
You said you wouldn't hurt her!

23
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:03,720
- You brat!
- Don't come any closer!

24
00:03:03,940 --> 00:03:05,220
This had nothing to do with you!

25
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,220
Huo Kaiming, don't come any closer!

26
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:09,820
You asked for this!

27
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:11,820
Songge!

28
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,660
Huo Kaiming!

29
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:13,780
Go away!

30
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,140
Go away!

31
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:16,140
Huo Kaiming!

32
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,780
I'll finish you off!

33
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:19,660
Time to die!

34
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,180
Songge!

35
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:34,300
- Songge!
- Chen Hui!

36
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:36,220
Songge!

37
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:37,740
Are you okay?

38
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:38,740
Untie me.

39
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:43,820
Get up.

40
00:04:08,780 --> 00:04:12,700
=Episode 19=
(The Illusion of Light)

41
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:13,940
(Uphold Justice)

42
00:04:13,940 --> 00:04:15,100
On the 27th of this month,

43
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:16,780
you called Yang Baichun.

44
00:04:16,780 --> 00:04:17,620
What did you say?

45
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,260
Mr. Yang had told me

46
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:21,660
that Zhangtou Village
had those kinds of courtyards.

47
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:22,580
I was curious,

48
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:24,180
so I asked him to take me there.

49
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:25,540
Then, why didn't you go?

50
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,780
My dad called me.

51
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:29,300
He said Huo Kaiming came back
and injured Mr. Huang.

52
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:30,460
He told me to get back.

53
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:32,100
What were you doing on the 27th?

54
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:34,100
On the 27th,

55
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:36,340
I was at the municipal hospital
getting dialysis.

56
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:37,740
Around 2:00 PM or so,

57
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:39,540
Chen Hui called me

58
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:40,820
and told me Huo Kaiming was back,

59
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:41,780
that we were in danger.

60
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:43,700
He told me not to go home,

61
00:04:43,700 --> 00:04:44,740
but to rest at a hotel

62
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:45,940
and wait for him to return.

63
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,060
On the 27th,

64
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:47,980
she stayed here.

65
00:04:47,980 --> 00:04:49,380
Did any of you see

66
00:04:49,380 --> 00:04:50,300
when she checked in?

67
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:52,500
We have so many guests every day,

68
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:53,440
I really can't remember.

69
00:04:53,450 --> 00:04:54,660
You went to the hotel
in the afternoon,

70
00:04:54,660 --> 00:04:55,580
but returned after nightfall.

71
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:56,980
Where were you during that time?

72
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:01,620
I took a nap during that time.

73
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:02,740
Almost 6:00 PM, I think?

74
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,600
I wanted to go out

75
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,740
and grab a bite.

76
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,300
I figured

77
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:07,700
they wouldn't catch Huo Kaiming

78
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:09,020
anytime soon.

79
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:11,220
I'd still have to stay
at the hotel for a while.

80
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:12,780
So I made a trip back home

81
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,220
to get some clothes.

82
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,860
When I got back to the hotel,

83
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,220
I ran into Limin.

84
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:19,500
So where did you go
after you found out Huo Kaiming had

85
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,340
injured Huang Liang?

86
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,900
I drove to Ping County.

87
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:22,740
Ping County?

88
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,500
What for?

89
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,480
Huang Liang is my partner
for the internet cafe.

90
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:28,180
The income

91
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:29,060
would go directly

92
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:30,100
into Huang Liang's account.

93
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:31,810
That account was opened

94
00:05:31,810 --> 00:05:32,860
at a bank in Ping County.

95
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:35,370
At the time, I didn't know
if Huang Liang was in danger.

96
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:37,020
So I didn't go to Zhangtou Village.

97
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,780
I headed to Ping County instead.

98
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:40,340
Thought I'd withdraw the money...

99
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:41,420
And transfer it

100
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:43,020
to my own account.

101
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,180
That was my idea.

102
00:05:45,180 --> 00:05:46,030
Why did you

103
00:05:46,030 --> 00:05:47,140
open an account so far away?

104
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:48,900
I was in prison at the time.

105
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:50,220
The bank procedures

106
00:05:50,220 --> 00:05:51,780
were very troublesome to handle.

107
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:52,620
It just so happened

108
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,140
I had a friend

109
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:55,540
who worked at that bank.

110
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,300
We found out that you didn't make

111
00:05:57,300 --> 00:05:58,140
any transfer

112
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,140
at the bank that day.

113
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,300
Because when I got there,

114
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:01,260
the bank was closed.

115
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,810
Why didn't you go later either?

116
00:06:02,980 --> 00:06:04,060
When I went home that night,

117
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:05,050
my dad told me

118
00:06:05,050 --> 00:06:06,030
Huang Liang was fine.

119
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:07,780
So, there was no need

120
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:08,940
to take it out.

121
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,820
What time did Chen Hui

122
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:12,220
get back to your house that night?

123
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,780
It should have been

124
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:15,740
around 9:00 PM.

125
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,460
Definitely before 9:30 PM.

126
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,620
Because the second episode
of the TV drama

127
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:20,460
wasn't over yet.

128
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:33,660
(People's Public Security)

129
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:41,020
(Jiangbin Public Security)

130
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:41,980
How did it go?

131
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,300
By the rules, I have to recuse myself.

132
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:51,380
How could they tell me

133
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:53,180
the details of their case?

134
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,740
Are you happy now?

135
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:01,060
Don't think I don't know

136
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:02,940
that you've been

137
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:05,820
investigating Hui all this time.

138
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:08,180
It's the municipal
PSB investigating him.

139
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:09,190
If you hadn't

140
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:10,460
pushed Hui this far,

141
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,100
would he have gotten

142
00:07:12,100 --> 00:07:13,140
mixed up with Yang Baichun?

143
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:16,710
Why would I push him for no reason?

144
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:20,500
Chen Hongbing.

145
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:23,380
I really don't understand.

146
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:25,980
I barely know you anymore.

147
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:28,420
Hui

148
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:30,820
is such a good kid.

149
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,900
We had such a wonderful family.

150
00:07:36,740 --> 00:07:37,580
Here in Fengyang,

151
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:39,780
everyone was jealous of us.

152
00:07:42,140 --> 00:07:44,260
Why do you have to be like this?

153
00:07:53,580 --> 00:07:54,900
Master. Mrs. Chen.

154
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:56,580
It's all cleared up.

155
00:07:58,380 --> 00:07:59,250
What do you mean?

156
00:07:59,250 --> 00:08:00,100
It's fine now.

157
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:00,980
Hui can leave

158
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:01,820
after the paperwork.

159
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,010
Is it really over?

160
00:08:04,010 --> 00:08:04,860
Master,

161
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,200
the suspicion has been cleared.

162
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,360
We investigated the members
of that prostitution ring

163
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,980
Director Tong arrested that night.

164
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:11,540
Three of them can prove

165
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,660
that around 9:00 PM.

166
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:13,740
Yang Baichun

167
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:15,340
drove his Santana

168
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,580
past their entrance twice.

169
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:17,780
Hui was already home by then.

170
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:19,700
He never had the time.

171
00:08:21,540 --> 00:08:22,380
Thank goodness.

172
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,220
Thank you.

173
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,370
Master, don't mention it.

174
00:08:24,370 --> 00:08:25,220
Madam, it's fine now.

175
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:26,060
- Don't worry.
- Thank you.

176
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:27,010
Thank you.

177
00:08:27,010 --> 00:08:27,860
It's nothing.

178
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:38,540
Director Chen is back.

179
00:08:38,540 --> 00:08:39,380
Hello.

180
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:44,180
Liang.

181
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:45,780
Hongbing.

182
00:08:45,780 --> 00:08:46,620
Mrs. Chen.

183
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,420
Why are you here?

184
00:08:48,420 --> 00:08:49,700
Did the doctor discharge you?

185
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:51,380
I'm mostly

186
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:52,500
healed up now.

187
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:53,540
I'm here to explain to you

188
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:54,650
what's going on

189
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,140
between me and Hui.

190
00:08:59,020 --> 00:08:59,860
Let's talk inside.

191
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:01,860
Come on. Let's go inside.

192
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:06,300
Come on.

193
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:07,460
Come on in.

194
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,820
Have a seat.

195
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:13,860
I'll get you a glass of water.

196
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,060
Don't trouble yourself.

197
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:16,140
It's no trouble at all.

198
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:18,660
About Huo Kaiming...

199
00:09:18,660 --> 00:09:19,660
Don't mention it to her.

200
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:21,140
I don't want her worrying about Hui.

201
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:21,980
Got it.

202
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:26,660
I heard you have a stake

203
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:27,700
in Hui's internet cafe.

204
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:29,180
At the time,

205
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:30,500
Hui told me

206
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,940
not to tell you about it just yet.

207
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,100
I figured it made sense.

208
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:35,020
As an ex-con,

209
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,660
going into business with your son

210
00:09:36,660 --> 00:09:37,660
would make you look bad,

211
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:38,500
Hongbing.

212
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:40,500
But I later realized

213
00:09:40,940 --> 00:09:41,780
how bad things were

214
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:43,700
between you two.

215
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:46,400
But the business was
already up and running.

216
00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:47,480
My hands were tied.

217
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:48,750
Hongbing, Mrs. Chen,

218
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:50,930
I always meant
to tell you about this.

219
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:51,820
But I didn't expect

220
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:53,220
so much to happen.

221
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,540
I never got the chance.

222
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:57,540
Huang Liang.

223
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:58,500
It's really fine.

224
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,780
That's all in the past.

225
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:01,500
Our family is doing great now.

226
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:02,580
No need to feel guilty.

227
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:04,940
So you and Hui

228
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:06,020
have made up?

229
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:07,620
No need to worry

230
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:08,900
about our family matters.

231
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:10,900
Hongbing.

232
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:11,740
Mrs. Chen.

233
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:13,340
Here's what I was thinking.

234
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:14,220
I'm going to be

235
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:15,210
discharged soon.

236
00:10:15,210 --> 00:10:16,060
I was thinking

237
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,540
of inviting Hui and Songge,

238
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:18,500
and all of us could

239
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:19,500
get together for a bit.

240
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,580
Sure.

241
00:10:25,180 --> 00:10:27,100
Chen Hui has been cleared
as a suspect for now.

242
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:28,700
By the way,

243
00:10:29,420 --> 00:10:31,060
when will we get
the DNA test results

244
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:31,980
of the crime scene's blood?

245
00:10:31,990 --> 00:10:33,300
It rained that day.

246
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:35,100
The blood was not only diluted,

247
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:36,500
but also biologically degraded.

248
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,310
Tang said it could take
at least four weeks.

249
00:10:38,330 --> 00:10:39,300
- Four weeks?
- Yes.

250
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:40,700
Tell Tang to rush it.

251
00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:42,900
This blood

252
00:10:42,900 --> 00:10:44,500
either belongs to Huo Kaiming,

253
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:45,820
(Owner of Blood at Scene)
or a third person.

254
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:46,660
(Who is the Killer?)
We still need to

255
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:48,380
(Did the Injured Die?)
track down Huo Kaiming.

256
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:49,940
Limin,

257
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:50,780
you're in charge of

258
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:52,260
tracking down Huo Kaiming.

259
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,100
Got it.

260
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:54,060
Also,

261
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,860
with such an amount
of blood at the scene,

262
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:57,380
we still haven't
found the murder weapon.

263
00:10:57,380 --> 00:10:58,240
While you're looking

264
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,300
for traces of Huo Kaiming,

265
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:01,580
use the coking plant as the center.

266
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:02,660
Expand the search radius

267
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:03,500
for the weapon.

268
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:06,340
If we find either of these,
we'll have a breakthrough.

269
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:07,580
Chief Guo.

270
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:08,580
I think we should

271
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:09,540
(Confirmed model of stun baton)
start by tracing the stun baton.

272
00:11:09,540 --> 00:11:10,860
The injury on Yang Baichun

273
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:12,530
was caused by this XR-5000

274
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:13,580
(Electric shock wound)
standard-issue stun baton.

275
00:11:13,580 --> 00:11:16,060
Every single one of these batons
is registered with our bureau.

276
00:11:16,420 --> 00:11:17,280
So I think

277
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,220
if we track this baton,

278
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:19,070
we can find out

279
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:20,540
(Burned vehicle at the scene)
who the third person at the scene was.

280
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:24,580
Cao.

281
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:27,260
Chief Guo.

282
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:28,900
Follow the stun baton lead.

283
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:30,020
Check the security departments

284
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:31,660
of the major factories
and mines in the city.

285
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:33,100
See who has them.

286
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,420
If you find anything suspicious,

287
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,300
report it immediately.

288
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:36,420
Understood, Chief Guo.

289
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,340
Huo Kaiming.

290
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:47,380
Today I saw

291
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:48,500
that the street

292
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,780
behind our clinic

293
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:51,420
has been completely fenced off.

294
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:53,110
They say it's going
to be demolished soon.

295
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,580
Not just that.

296
00:11:56,660 --> 00:11:57,620
The mine is currently

297
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:00,780
scaling back production.

298
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:03,500
A lot of the old buildings and facilities

299
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,300
are being reclaimed for redevelopment.

300
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:09,180
How did this happen?

301
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,980
How does such a massive enterprise

302
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:11,980
just disappear?

303
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:13,900
Isn't that normal?

304
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:17,060
Nothing in this world
stays the same forever.

305
00:12:19,700 --> 00:12:20,900
Let me remind you,

306
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:21,860
when we go in later

307
00:12:21,860 --> 00:12:23,180
and see Hui and Songge,

308
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:24,780
talk a bit more.

309
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:27,300
We'll see.

310
00:12:27,300 --> 00:12:29,200
What do you mean by that?

311
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:31,100
Huang Liang was nice enough to invite us.

312
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:32,060
You know exactly

313
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:32,970
what he's trying to do.

314
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:34,850
If you keep scowling,

315
00:12:34,850 --> 00:12:35,700
I'm not going to be

316
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:36,620
nice to you anymore.

317
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:39,100
Whatever you say.

318
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:40,020
That's more like it.

319
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:40,860
Let's go.

320
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,420
Dad. Mom.

321
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:43,680
- Mr. Chen, Mrs. Chen.
- Hui is here.

322
00:12:43,690 --> 00:12:44,960
- Uncle Huang.
- Look at you.

323
00:12:44,970 --> 00:12:46,030
You're just coming for a meal,

324
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:47,220
why did you bring so much stuff?

325
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:48,070
Honestly.

326
00:12:48,070 --> 00:12:48,940
Come sit down.

327
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,060
Hurry.

328
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:04,780
Today,

329
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,700
to celebrate my discharge
from the hospital,

330
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:08,060
I invited your whole family over.

331
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:09,020
So we could all

332
00:13:09,020 --> 00:13:10,820
get together

333
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:11,660
and have a nice meal.

334
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:21,100
Tell you what.

335
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:22,700
I'll raise a toast with my tea.

336
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:24,060
Let's have a toast first, alright?

337
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:24,980
Sounds good.

338
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,180
Come on.

339
00:13:26,180 --> 00:13:27,070
Come on, Songge.

340
00:13:27,190 --> 00:13:28,060
Let's all drink.

341
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:29,060
Hongbing.

342
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:31,500
Mrs. Chen.

343
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:36,580
Sit down, everyone.

344
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,820
Everyone, have a seat.

345
00:13:37,820 --> 00:13:39,180
Hongbing, enjoy the food.

346
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:40,020
Okay.

347
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:41,180
Hongbing.

348
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:42,020
Try this.

349
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:44,380
I can handle it.

350
00:13:47,140 --> 00:13:48,180
I'm here to serve you.

351
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:50,140
Hello, Dr. Liu.

352
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:56,420
Really?

353
00:13:57,740 --> 00:13:59,060
That's wonderful.

354
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:00,130
Thank you, Dr. Liu.

355
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:01,060
Thank you!

356
00:14:01,260 --> 00:14:02,100
We'll head over now.

357
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:02,940
We're on our way.

358
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:05,340
Songge.

359
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,340
They found a kidney.

360
00:14:06,340 --> 00:14:07,620
We finally got a kidney for you!

361
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:12,460
You got a kidney?

362
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,540
Then hurry and get to the hospital!

363
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:15,740
- Hurry up and go!
- Yes!

364
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:17,540
The doctor wants to do another
check-up and dialysis.

365
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:18,400
We're heading over now.

366
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,300
You guys carry on.

367
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:20,140
Songge.

368
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,180
Sweetie.

369
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:26,780
Don't be nervous.

370
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:30,020
Everything will be fine.

371
00:14:30,020 --> 00:14:30,860
My wife and I

372
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:33,140
will always be here for you.

373
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:37,700
Sir.

374
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:39,940
Does this mean Hui and I

375
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:41,260
can come back for dinner again?

376
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,300
Of course.

377
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:57,860
Thank you, sir.

378
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:01,740
Thank you, Dad.

379
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:03,180
We'll be going now.

380
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:05,180
Go on, hurry.

381
00:15:14,220 --> 00:15:18,700
(Jiangbin People's Hospital)

382
00:15:25,420 --> 00:15:26,650
- Songge.
- Mr. Chen, Mrs. Chen.

383
00:15:26,650 --> 00:15:28,110
- Mom.
- Why are you guys here so early?

384
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:30,140
Of course we had to get here early.

385
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:33,100
Dad, did you ask Director Tong
for time off today?

386
00:15:33,740 --> 00:15:34,970
I took two days off.

387
00:15:34,970 --> 00:15:35,820
How is it?

388
00:15:35,820 --> 00:15:37,620
Are Songge's pre-op test results

389
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:38,460
all out?

390
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:40,060
I'll go check.

391
00:15:40,060 --> 00:15:41,370
Songge, the thermometer is ready.

392
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:45,180
Here.

393
00:15:51,940 --> 00:15:52,940
I'll go with him.

394
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:00,260
Mrs. Chen.

395
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:07,980
Nervous?

396
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:13,260
It's okay.

397
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:14,500
It's normal to be nervous.

398
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,420
This is a big decision.

399
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:17,300
Anyone would be

400
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:18,260
just as nervous.

401
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:19,660
To tell you the truth,

402
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:21,580
I'm nervous too.

403
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:23,020
Even more nervous

404
00:16:23,020 --> 00:16:24,700
than the first time
I gave someone a shot.

405
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:26,940
Mrs. Chen.

406
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:29,100
You're a doctor.

407
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:30,380
How can you be nervous?

408
00:16:30,380 --> 00:16:31,420
Of course I am.

409
00:16:31,420 --> 00:16:32,460
You're family.

410
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:40,620
Mrs. Chen.

411
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,980
Thank you and Mr. Chen.

412
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:45,820
Don't think about anything else.

413
00:16:45,820 --> 00:16:47,510
Just focus
on getting through the surgery.

414
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,140
You will always be

415
00:16:49,460 --> 00:16:50,300
a child

416
00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:51,740
of our family.

417
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,020
You got this.

418
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:00,180
You got this.

419
00:17:03,020 --> 00:17:04,460
(Operating Room)

420
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:18,260
Why do you look
even more nervous than I am?

421
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:23,060
We'll be waiting for you.

422
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,540
Songge.

423
00:17:27,540 --> 00:17:28,380
You got this.

424
00:17:50,940 --> 00:17:53,020
(In Operation)

425
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:54,180
It's fine.

426
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:55,620
They've been

427
00:17:55,620 --> 00:17:57,300
doing this kind of surgery
for many years.

428
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:58,940
Usually, nothing goes wrong.

429
00:17:58,940 --> 00:17:59,860
Don't be nervous.

430
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:02,420
Am I the one who's nervous,

431
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:03,580
or are you?

432
00:18:08,900 --> 00:18:14,260
(In Operation)
(Operating Room)

433
00:18:15,340 --> 00:18:18,180
(People's Public Security)

434
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:21,300
(As the 1998
Chinese New Year approaches,)

435
00:18:21,300 --> 00:18:22,860
(Jiangbin Radio Station)

436
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:25,700
(wishes everyone in the city
a happy Chinese New Year,)

437
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,460
(and a joyous family reunion!)

438
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:28,300
Hongbing.

439
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:29,220
How's Songge's

440
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:30,660
recovery doing now?

441
00:18:31,820 --> 00:18:34,580
The doctor says
she's recovering incredibly well.

442
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:35,660
She's young, after all.

443
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:37,980
She looks so much better now than she did

444
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:38,980
a few years ago.

445
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:41,780
That's double the good news.

446
00:18:41,780 --> 00:18:42,980
We really should celebrate.

447
00:18:44,740 --> 00:18:45,580
Hongbing.

448
00:18:45,580 --> 00:18:46,980
During these few days
of Chinese New Year,

449
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:47,990
don't take any shifts.

450
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:48,900
I'll cover them.

451
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:49,940
That doesn't feel right.

452
00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:52,420
I've worked Chinese New Year's Eve
every year.

453
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:53,500
If you suddenly

454
00:18:53,500 --> 00:18:54,660
let me off this year,

455
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:55,500
it'll feel strange.

456
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:56,340
Come on.

457
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:57,780
Let me do it.

458
00:18:57,780 --> 00:18:59,260
You just go home and relax.

459
00:18:59,260 --> 00:19:00,460
Your family hasn't had

460
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:02,020
a moment of peace all year.

461
00:19:03,460 --> 00:19:05,860
Spend some quality time with them.

462
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:09,260
Alright.

463
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,780
Then, I'll leave it to you.

464
00:19:10,780 --> 00:19:11,620
If anything comes up,

465
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:13,220
give me a call.

466
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:14,060
Don't worry.

467
00:19:14,060 --> 00:19:15,020
I'll call if I need you.

468
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:17,340
Thanks.

469
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:18,420
Go on.

470
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,260
Okay.

471
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:25,740
All set.

472
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:28,740
Songge.

473
00:19:28,740 --> 00:19:30,020
No, stop doing that.

474
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:31,770
Give it to me.

475
00:19:31,770 --> 00:19:32,680
I'm fine, Mrs. Chen.

476
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,820
I'm fully recovered.

477
00:19:34,100 --> 00:19:35,020
No.

478
00:19:35,020 --> 00:19:36,200
I talked to the doctor.

479
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,190
You need to rest up

480
00:19:37,190 --> 00:19:38,110
for a year or two.

481
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:39,460
Here.

482
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:45,580
This is too wet.

483
00:19:45,580 --> 00:19:46,440
Wring it out more.

484
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,460
Wring it out.

485
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:48,340
It's dry enough!

486
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:49,280
Just wring it once more.

487
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:50,810
By the way, Songge,

488
00:19:50,810 --> 00:19:51,670
Hui.

489
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:52,950
Hui's dad and I talked it over.

490
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,260
For this Chinese New Year,

491
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:56,060
don't bother coming
back to Fengyang.

492
00:19:56,060 --> 00:19:56,940
We will come here.

493
00:19:56,940 --> 00:19:58,180
Save Songge the trip.

494
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:59,530
I'm really fine, Mrs. Chen.

495
00:19:59,620 --> 00:20:00,980
Let us go back to Fengyang.

496
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:02,540
Yeah, Mom.

497
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:04,260
After all, Fengyang is our home.

498
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:06,740
Alright.

499
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:08,060
We'll do what Hui says.

500
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:10,420
We can celebrate
as long as the family is together.

501
00:20:10,420 --> 00:20:11,380
That's what matters.

502
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:12,220
Yeah.

503
00:20:14,340 --> 00:20:15,180
You're back!

504
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,020
Mr. Chen.

505
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:17,780
Let me take that.

506
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:18,780
I bought some fruit.

507
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:19,620
Hui!

508
00:20:19,740 --> 00:20:20,580
Firecrackers.

509
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:22,100
Don't let Songge carry those!

510
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:22,980
It's fine.

511
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:23,820
The sound will drive

512
00:20:23,820 --> 00:20:24,660
the bad luck away.

513
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:26,530
Mr. Chen, don't you remember

514
00:20:26,530 --> 00:20:28,140
Hui is terrified of firecrackers.

515
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:30,700
When he was little,
he'd want to hide under the covers.

516
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:32,260
He's grown up now, hasn't he?

517
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:33,420
No way.

518
00:20:33,420 --> 00:20:34,340
I'm not scared at all.

519
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,460
Then, you're in charge
of setting them off.

520
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:38,220
I'll go wash the fruit first.

521
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,860
I'll go wash the fruit too.

522
00:20:42,140 --> 00:20:43,780
The Liugou Coking Plant
in Fengyang Town

523
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:44,620
will need

524
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:46,380
a closer look.

525
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:48,960
The DNA test results

526
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:51,500
from the blood at the scene
show it's Huo Kaiming's.

527
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,500
Judging by the amount of blood lost,

528
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:54,780
Huo Kaiming is likely dead.

529
00:20:55,780 --> 00:20:56,620
But the problem is,

530
00:20:57,140 --> 00:20:57,980
even now,

531
00:20:58,740 --> 00:20:59,980
we still haven't found him.

532
00:21:00,540 --> 00:21:01,380
Also,

533
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:03,340
(Electric shock wound)
Yang Baichun's mental state

534
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:04,740
shows no signs of recovery.

535
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:06,780
Cao.

536
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:08,540
Anything on the stun baton?

537
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:10,500
We've been
looking into it for two months.

538
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:11,410
It's almost impossible.

539
00:21:11,860 --> 00:21:13,100
This model of stun baton

540
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,500
started production in 1983.

541
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:16,410
A lot of security departments
in factories and mines,

542
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:19,060
even quality assurance committees
of larger farming communes,

543
00:21:19,060 --> 00:21:19,900
were issued them.

544
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:21,300
Over the years, many were

545
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,410
broken, lost,

546
00:21:22,410 --> 00:21:23,550
or unaccounted for.

547
00:21:24,060 --> 00:21:26,780
If the one we're looking for
came from another province,

548
00:21:26,780 --> 00:21:27,700
then it's even harder.

549
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:33,100
Let's not get discouraged yet.

550
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,260
Let's think about

551
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:35,100
a different angle

552
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:36,260
we can investigate from.

553
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:39,620
(Heyi Coal Washing Plant, Fengyang Town.
Please excuse the renovation.)

554
00:22:14,940 --> 00:22:16,220
Someone...

555
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:18,300
There's a dead body!

556
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:20,350
There's a dead body
in the coal washing pool!

557
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:21,820
There's a dead body!

558
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:31,180
The body's all bloated.

559
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,940
It's completely unrecognizable.

560
00:22:35,780 --> 00:22:36,620
Wait, Chief Guo.

561
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:44,500
It's Huo Kaiming.

562
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:53,740
Okay.

563
00:22:53,940 --> 00:22:54,780
Transport the body

564
00:22:54,780 --> 00:22:55,620
back to the bureau.

565
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:56,770
Have the forensics examine it

566
00:22:56,780 --> 00:22:58,620
to determine the time
and cause of death.

567
00:22:58,780 --> 00:22:59,620
Also,

568
00:22:59,620 --> 00:23:01,340
take some men and search the area.

569
00:23:01,340 --> 00:23:02,540
See if there are more clues.

570
00:23:03,900 --> 00:23:04,740
Chief Guo.

571
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:05,940
There's something else

572
00:23:05,940 --> 00:23:06,900
you should know.

573
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:08,460
This place

574
00:23:08,460 --> 00:23:09,330
is where we found

575
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:11,380
a huge stash of cough syrup before.

576
00:23:11,690 --> 00:23:12,630
Someone even tried

577
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:13,700
to dredge up syrup here.

578
00:23:13,820 --> 00:23:14,980
But we didn't catch the guy.

579
00:23:15,980 --> 00:23:16,860
Any suspects?

580
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:18,300
Yes.

581
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:20,140
Director Chen suspected

582
00:23:20,780 --> 00:23:21,620
it was Chen Hui.

583
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:22,780
Chen Hui?

584
00:23:24,300 --> 00:23:26,100
Let's hurry up. Or else
the supermarket will be closed.

585
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:26,940
Yeah.

586
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:28,740
Get in the car first.

587
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:29,580
Okay.

588
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,660
Mrs. Chen, you go first.

589
00:23:31,060 --> 00:23:31,900
Careful, Songge.

590
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:34,560
Hui.

591
00:23:34,560 --> 00:23:36,440
It's about time you returned the car.

592
00:23:36,660 --> 00:23:37,860
Mr. Huang is back now.

593
00:23:37,860 --> 00:23:38,780
You're still driving it.

594
00:23:38,780 --> 00:23:39,780
It's not nice.

595
00:23:39,780 --> 00:23:40,660
I know.

596
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:44,540
What a beautiful car.

597
00:23:44,540 --> 00:23:45,700
Never seen anything

598
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:46,540
like it.

599
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:48,020
Really amazing.

600
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:49,060
How about

601
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:49,900
you drive today?

602
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:51,260
Can I?

603
00:23:51,260 --> 00:23:52,200
Why not?

604
00:23:52,460 --> 00:23:53,300
How thoughtful.

605
00:23:53,300 --> 00:23:54,540
Let me open the door for you.

606
00:23:57,660 --> 00:23:58,700
You're driving?

607
00:23:58,700 --> 00:24:00,020
Can you handle it?

608
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:00,940
Just giving it a try.

609
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:01,780
Look at this.

610
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:04,660
What's going on?

611
00:24:04,660 --> 00:24:05,860
Why is it getting so cramped?

612
00:24:05,860 --> 00:24:07,340
Just press the button and it'll stop.

613
00:24:07,340 --> 00:24:08,430
- Really?
- This car has

614
00:24:08,430 --> 00:24:09,420
seat memory.

615
00:24:09,420 --> 00:24:11,460
The manual controls are the two buttons
on the side.

616
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:12,860
So advanced.

617
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:22,300
Back up.

618
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:26,060
(Limin.)

619
00:24:26,130 --> 00:24:27,010
(Master.)

620
00:24:27,010 --> 00:24:27,970
Did you find something?

621
00:24:39,900 --> 00:24:41,900
Let's buy some ground meat later.

622
00:24:41,900 --> 00:24:43,940
We'll have beef dumplings tonight.

623
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:45,100
Songge is a little anemic.

624
00:24:45,100 --> 00:24:45,940
She needs nutrients.

625
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:46,900
Thank you, Mrs. Chen.

626
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:48,180
Right.

627
00:24:48,180 --> 00:24:50,220
The Chinese New Year red envelopes
need to be prepared too.

628
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:52,740
We'll have Hui
go to the bank and get some crisp bills

629
00:24:52,740 --> 00:24:53,940
to put in the red envelopes.

630
00:24:53,940 --> 00:24:54,780
I'll go get it later.

631
00:24:54,780 --> 00:24:55,860
Don't you go.

632
00:24:55,860 --> 00:24:58,540
I have to keep an eye on you,
otherwise you'll just buy random stuff.

633
00:24:58,540 --> 00:24:59,500
Let your dad go.

634
00:25:02,060 --> 00:25:02,900
Chen Hongbing.

635
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:05,020
Why aren't you listening to me?

636
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:05,900
I'm listening.

637
00:25:06,340 --> 00:25:07,380
What did I just say?

638
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:08,740
I'm driving the car.

639
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:09,580
See?

640
00:25:09,940 --> 00:25:11,780
I told you to get some cash

641
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:13,260
for the red envelopes.

642
00:25:13,260 --> 00:25:15,260
Is it because
you're nervous driving this car?

643
00:25:15,260 --> 00:25:16,540
If you're nervous, let me drive.

644
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:17,740
Okay, stop messing around.

645
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:19,110
Alright, alright, I'll get the money.

646
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:20,040
I'll get it.

647
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:23,380
Beef dumplings...

648
00:25:23,380 --> 00:25:24,340
What else should I make?

649
00:25:25,380 --> 00:25:26,420
I'll braise some ribs.

650
00:25:28,820 --> 00:25:29,660
And make a fish.

651
00:25:41,380 --> 00:25:42,230
Come on, Songge.

652
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:48,620
Oh, right.

653
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:49,740
I just remembered.

654
00:25:49,740 --> 00:25:50,800
Director Tong will be away

655
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:51,740
this afternoon.

656
00:25:51,740 --> 00:25:52,780
I need to cover a shift for him.

657
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:53,840
Hui, tell you what.

658
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,300
I'll drive to the station.

659
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:56,820
After you guys finish shopping,

660
00:25:57,340 --> 00:25:58,340
just grab a cab back.

661
00:25:58,340 --> 00:25:59,740
It's the Chinese New Year.

662
00:25:59,740 --> 00:26:00,700
Why are you so busy?

663
00:26:00,700 --> 00:26:01,620
Cut me some slacks.

664
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:02,460
Fine.

665
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:03,380
Go on, then.

666
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:04,540
Come back early.

667
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:05,380
Okay.

668
00:26:05,460 --> 00:26:06,300
Let's go.

669
00:26:06,780 --> 00:26:07,620
Let's go.

670
00:26:24,620 --> 00:26:25,460
Limin.

671
00:26:26,140 --> 00:26:27,180
Start driving now.

672
00:26:28,020 --> 00:26:28,860
To the coking plant.

673
00:26:30,420 --> 00:26:31,260
Yes.

674
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:32,900
We'll talk when you get here.

675
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:53,100
Master.

676
00:26:54,460 --> 00:26:55,580
How long did it take you

677
00:26:55,580 --> 00:26:56,660
to get here from the city?

678
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:57,720
Two hours and ten minutes.

679
00:26:59,780 --> 00:27:01,460
It took me two hours
and fifteen minutes.

680
00:27:02,380 --> 00:27:03,220
Not much difference.

681
00:27:04,540 --> 00:27:05,460
Master.

682
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:06,300
What's going on?

683
00:27:07,980 --> 00:27:09,180
I suspect that the person

684
00:27:10,420 --> 00:27:12,060
who drove Yang Baichun's car here

685
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:14,060
that day

686
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:16,980
was a woman.

687
00:27:17,980 --> 00:27:18,940
A woman?

688
00:27:19,980 --> 00:27:20,950
That's impossible.

689
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:21,980
How could one woman

690
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:22,820
possibly take down

691
00:27:22,820 --> 00:27:23,660
two grown men?

692
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:26,460
It's very unlikely

693
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:27,420
to be a woman.

694
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:30,900
But what if there was

695
00:27:32,780 --> 00:27:34,260
a fourth person at the scene?

696
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:38,860
Master.

697
00:27:40,300 --> 00:27:41,460
I know what you're suspecting.

698
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:43,100
But if it's true...

699
00:27:48,100 --> 00:27:48,960
I'm also hoping

700
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,300
my suspicion is wrong.

701
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,660
Yang Baichun was seen

702
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:54,580
at 9:00 PM that night

703
00:27:54,580 --> 00:27:55,900
in Zhangtou Village.

704
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:58,140
Between 9:00 PM and 11:30 PM,

705
00:27:58,140 --> 00:27:59,740
that's only two and a half hours.

706
00:27:59,740 --> 00:28:01,420
In such a short amount of time,

707
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:02,540
driving over here,

708
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:03,820
setting the car on fire,

709
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:04,940
and getting back to the hotel

710
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:06,780
is practically impossible.

711
00:28:08,620 --> 00:28:10,100
You think it's impossible too, right?

712
00:28:10,100 --> 00:28:10,940
Impossible.

713
00:28:12,220 --> 00:28:13,260
Exactly.

714
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:14,300
Which means,

715
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:18,020
this person's alibi

716
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:19,340
is completely solid.

717
00:29:25,220 --> 00:29:26,060
Thanks, driver.

718
00:29:32,820 --> 00:29:33,660
Let's go.

719
00:29:35,810 --> 00:29:36,670
Come on, Songge.

720
00:29:47,540 --> 00:29:49,500
You are back so early.

721
00:29:49,500 --> 00:29:51,060
I thought you'd be later.

722
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:52,620
Okay, I'll get Chinese
New Year's Eve dinner ready.

723
00:29:52,620 --> 00:29:54,250
Go tidy up the house a bit later.

724
00:29:54,380 --> 00:29:55,370
Mrs. Chen, I'll help you.

725
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:56,780
Okay, let's go. Hand those to me.

726
00:29:56,780 --> 00:29:57,620
Okay.

727
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:58,460
Let's go.

728
00:29:58,780 --> 00:29:59,620
Hui.

729
00:30:02,630 --> 00:30:04,310
Light some joss sticks
for your grandfather.

730
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:16,740
Grandpa.

731
00:30:36,380 --> 00:30:37,220
Dad.

732
00:30:37,740 --> 00:30:38,580
What's wrong?

733
00:30:40,860 --> 00:30:41,700
Nothing.

734
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:53,980
You've grown so tall.

735
00:31:02,620 --> 00:31:03,460
Zhang?

736
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:40,260
Hui.

737
00:31:40,260 --> 00:31:41,940
I'm pretty much done here.

738
00:31:41,940 --> 00:31:43,140
How's the cleaning going on?

739
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:45,110
- I finished wiping the windows.
- Ding Yue! Ding Yue!

740
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:47,220
Zhang just called.

741
00:31:47,660 --> 00:31:48,500
His son Chubby

742
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:49,820
was setting off firecrackers

743
00:31:49,820 --> 00:31:51,180
and accidentally hurt his hand!

744
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:52,020
What should we do?

745
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:53,300
How could he be so careless?

746
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:54,380
I'll go take a look.

747
00:31:54,780 --> 00:31:55,620
Mrs. Chen.

748
00:31:55,620 --> 00:31:57,780
We'll wait until you get back
to cook the dumplings.

749
00:31:57,780 --> 00:31:58,830
No need. Don't wait for me.

750
00:31:59,020 --> 00:32:00,220
Just eat when they're ready.

751
00:32:00,780 --> 00:32:01,660
I'll be back soon.

752
00:32:02,100 --> 00:32:02,940
Be careful!
